  <brief_title>Effect of Mouthwash Containing Camellia Sinensis Extracts on Oral Malodor</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Mouthwash Containing Camellia Sinensis Extracts on Oral Malodor, Plaque and Papillary Bleeding Indices in Gingivitis Patients.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
